1454
01:24:15.712 --> 01:24:19.652
Number two, gives the maximum dose that you can to the tumor

1455
01:24:19.712 --> 01:24:23.472
microenvironment while still preserving about 20% of the tumor getting

1456
01:24:23.532 --> 01:24:24.412
